Nigerians have reacted to the reports of the Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie, having another child and marrying a new wife, consoling his first wife, May Edochie to be strong. Recall that the couple had recently celebrated their 17th wedding anniversary, the news of his second wife came as a shock to the general public. The actor via his Instagram page announced the existence of his son with his second wife who is a Nigerian actress, Judy Austin on Wednesday. His first wife while reacting to his post wrote, ““May God judge you both.” Her comment got so many reactions from Nigerians who sympathized with her. Here are some of the reactions gathered from the actor’s Instagram page; @recious.ijay wrote, “It is well, mummy, be consoled Nne. I blame Judy seriously.” @glad_godwins wrote, “It is well. So sorry ma.” POLL @annabelimaobong wrote, “My dear, may God comfort you on all sides at a time like this , I really feel your pains.” @adambolu wrote, “I am so sorry ma. As for you @yuledochie I am so disappointed with you chai.” @daniellanelson88 wrote, “Mummy, take heart na you I know, I don’t no any other person.” @rachaelwezziewawophiri wrote, “No its painful. I truly understand your pain mary.” @jeybrenda wrote, “It’s well ma. @kate_janet_ogalo wrote, “I feel hurt on your behalf.”